reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect! Just as Pictured!
reviews.reviewText: When this arrived, I was shocked how small the box was to have TWO end tables inside. Sure enough, there were two! It was extremely easy to assemble them and they work great! Exactly as advertised and good quality. I can not believe how affordable these end tables were! Please note that these end tables are intended to be for a bit of a smaller space, which is what I was looking for. So make sure to check the measurements of the space you are trying to place them in!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars We loved the functionality
reviews.reviewText: This was a very economical way to get things organized in a preteen space.Good value and so easy to assemble!We actually bought 2 sets of these and found that they actually make great gifts.The handy place to charge several items is a feature favorite. My sister said, "I really use these tables a lot more than I thought I would, so glad you gave them to me. I don't have to seek the wall plug behind the headboard and change it frequently, you always find just the right solutions."I felt like a hero! I plan to purchase more of these.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Not as advertised
reviews.reviewText: Overall the item works nicely for my space and is a good price, however it is advertised as a clean, screw free top. As you can see from my photo, there are four screws that show on the top. I don't find that very attractive.When I contacted the vendor they responded with, "I am so sorry for that, and maybe its a mistake to us. And we have improved this product without the srewhole. But maybe our warehouse place a few of end table with srewhole by mistake, so we can not make sure that if you will get a new end table without screwhole. So I hope that you can accept some refund for $3 or more if there are not other problems to the end table. Looking forward to your reply, have a nice day."There are so many positive reviews and yet no one is bothered by the screw showing on top? It would be OK if the photo showed that, but clearly it does not. I would have thought twice if the photo showed what it really looks like on top.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Its a small side table
reviews.reviewText: This side table was so easy to assemble. I purchased a set of two and it arrived well packaged with no damage. All the pieces are numbered and the screws etc are put in each individual bag with the alphabet on the bag to go with the numbered piece. They also put all screws etc for one side table in a big bag with all needed to assemble it, so two bags with all that is needed for the two side table assemble.Now I can plug my phone in and laptop or whatever I need to.Its not big so if you want a side table thats big this is not for you but if small is in order this is the one. It does seem well made and the pictures are pretty accurate on amazon.
Bought these for my boys they love them and come in handy for charging all their devices bedside

Bought this set for the wife and I because of price and features. It was pretty straightforward assembling the stands, and took about 30 minutes. All tools needed were included! Plugged them in, and the USB ports are decent quality, as well, the power port. Up close the finish is rather cheap looking, but from a distance, they look fine. It is on the small side, but that is perfect for us. It is rather sturdy and the fastenings are decent. Adjustable rubber feet allow leveling of the table top. For the price, I thought worth every penny. I will be buying another set for the kids room. If you are looking for an economical nightstand set, this is your choice. Just be sure to check the dimensions so you know what you are buying.
